SUBJECT: Turn your Facebook page into a business & make $600 USD daily
Dear sir/madam,
This email is with regard to an earlier one sent to you concerning “Do you
have a Facebook page? Do you know you can turn your Facebook page into a
business that can make $600 USD daily?” Here is the answer with Skin
Transforma. Skin Transforma, a leading manufacturer of glutathione for skin
beauty, we seek reliable persons to fill vacancies as zonal distributor
specialist due to logistic difficulties we face when dealing from your
area. So, the management has decided to enlist the service of individuals.
How does this work?
1. First you will choose a business name and white label of your choice
which you will make your Facebook Page that we will connect to your online
store, we will build an online ecommerce store for you to match your
Facebook page.
2. After that, we will BOAST your page, and all our customers from your
country will order from your online store and make payment directly to you,
from the product we will supply to you, you will be entitled to a
commission-based wage of 7% on every distribution.
3. Any amount generated from your Facebook page is 100% yours.
Upon receipt of your response, our legal team will provide the necessary
legal framework for your new business. In the meantime, please provide a
number you can be reached at so we can have a staff call you
Regards
Jane
Zonal Coordinator
Skin Transforma
From: m*****8@gmail.com
To: u*****8@mail.wltechinc.top
Time: 2023-02-28 20:57:55
SUBJECT: Please respond with your willingness to proceed
Dear,
We appreciate your interest in our offer and would like for you to know
more about this. At Skin Transforma Supply, we are primarily involved in
the manufacture of glutathione for skin beauty, we seek your service as a
distributor Specialist in your area due to logistic difficulties we face
when dealing from your country.
Skin Transforma Supply is a company listed on the ESE {European Stock
Exchange}, with over 300 employees. As a distributor Specialist in your
country, you will be distributing goods from the goods we will ship to you
to distribute to customers that make orders from your online store. Your
functions shall not require you to move about distributing goods or go to
an office, it is a very flexible job to enable you have time for your other
regular job and other activities.
Payment orders, checks, and electronic payments would be made to your
business or personal name, and in the case of wire transfers, a dedicated
bank account would be used so as not to mix up company funds with your
other personal income. For your services, (you will be entitled to a
commission-based wage of 7% on every distribution you make). Please be
informed that payments for supplies from customers are usually NOT LESS
THAN $20,000 (twenty thousand dollars), and could be as much as 8 to 10
times in a 4-week period.
After each received payment clears, you would be required to transfer to
our consolidated trade account, less your commission. If the above stated
terms are okay with you, please respond with your willingness to proceed,
as to enable us to set up your online store.
